// Test GenModel: try_unroll_loop handles sgt (reverse loop) condition
//
// Verifies that a reverse loop `for (i = 3; i > -1; i--)` with trip_count=4
// is unrolled correctly by GenModel's try_unroll_loop (sgt predicate).
// The loop body adds %data to the accumulator 4 times (i=3,2,1,0).
//
// RUN: %hirct-gen %S/../../fixtures/UnrollLoopSgt.mlir -o %t --only model
// RUN: cat %t/cmodel/UnrollLoopSgt.cpp | %FileCheck %s
//
// CHECK: AUTO-GENERATED
// CHECK: void UnrollLoopSgt::eval_comb()
// Loop is unrolled 4 times, each iteration adds data to accumulator.
// CHECK-COUNT-4: + (data)
